    <item>
      <title>伦敦的房屋变得越来越负担得起，但对于许多人来说是遥不可及的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/london-house-prices-become-cheaper-but-are-still-unaffordable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦的房屋是他们十年来最实惠的房屋，但对于许多人来说仍然是遥不可及的，强调了工党政府在解决英国住房危机方面面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/london-house-prices-become-cheaper-but-are-still-unaffordable</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 12:04:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前犹他州众议员米娅·洛夫（Mia Love）是第一位当选美国众议院的黑人共和党妇女</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-24/former-utah-rep-mia-love-the-first-black-republican-woman-elected-to-the-us-house-has-died</link>
      <description><![CDATA[盐湖城（AP）＆Mdash;前美国众议员米娅·洛夫（Mia Love）犹他州是海地移民的女儿，后者成为第一位当选国会的黑人共和党妇女，他于周日去世。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-24/former-utah-rep-mia-love-the-first-black-republican-woman-elected-to-the-us-house-has-died</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 02:58:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
